{"text_id":61731,"tokens":["This"," paper"," addresses"," the"," problem"," of"," training"," deep"," neural"," networks"," by"," proposing"," a"," new"," optimization"," algorithm"," called"," Entropy","-","SGD","."," The"," algorithm"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," local"," geometry"," of"," the"," energy"," landscape",","," which"," suggests"," that"," local"," extrema"," with"," low"," generalization"," error"," have"," a"," large"," proportion"," of"," almost","-","zero"," eigenvalues"," in"," the"," Hessian"," with"," very"," few"," positive"," or"," negative"," eigenvalues","."," The"," paper"," then"," lever","ages"," this"," observation"," to"," construct"," a"," local","-","entropy","-","based"," objective"," function"," that"," favors"," well","-","general","izable"," solutions"," while"," avoiding"," poorly","-","general","izable"," solutions",".","\n\n","Strengths"," of"," the"," paper"," include"," the"," clear"," and"," detailed"," description"," of"," the"," algorithm",","," the"," thorough"," analysis"," of"," the"," energy"," landscape",","," and"," the"," convincing"," experimental"," results","."," The"," paper"," also"," provides"," a"," clear"," explanation"," of"," the"," assumptions"," and"," limitations"," of"," the"," proposed"," algorithm",".","\n\n","Weaknesses"," of"," the"," paper"," include"," the"," lack"," of"," comparison"," to"," other"," optimization"," algorithms"," and"," the"," limited"," discussion"," of"," the"," theoretical"," implications"," of"," the"," proposed"," algorithm","."," Additionally",","," the"," paper"," could"," benefit"," from"," a"," more"," detailed"," discussion"," of"," the"," potential"," applications"," of"," the"," proposed"," algorithm","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"davinci","label":1}